Preferred local project path:

```text
.cursor/skills/index-valuation-rotation
```

Workflow:

1. Read `.cursor/skills/index-valuation-rotation/SKILL.md`.
2. Use the Pandadata API skill at `.cursor/skills/pandadata-api` to verify exact `panda_data` method parameters and fields before calling any API.
